---
---

<section class="ecosystem-section" id="ecosystem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        技术生态
      </span>
      <h2 class="section-title">smartboot 技术生态</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        构建完整解决方案，提供全栈技术支持
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="ecosystem-grid">
      <a href="https://smartboot.tech/smart-socket/" target="_blank" class="ecosystem-card">
        <div class="card-border"></div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="project-tag">网络通信</span>
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M7 7h10v10"/>
              <path d="M7 17 17 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>smart-socket</h3>
          <p>Java AIO 实现的支持百万级长连接通信框架</p>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="explore-link">
              探索项目
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://smartboot.tech/feat/" target="_blank" class="ecosystem-card featured">
        <div class="card-border"></div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="project-tag">Web框架</span>
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M7 7h10v10"/>
              <path d="M7 17 17 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>feat</h3>
          <p>运行性能超 Vert.x，开发体验近似 SpringBoot，以 AI 原生和云原生双引擎驱动的现代化 Java Web 服务开发框架</p>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="explore-link">
              探索项目
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://smartboot.tech/smart-mqtt/" target="_blank" class="ecosystem-card">
        <div class="card-border"></div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="project-tag">物联网</span>
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M7 7h10v10"/>
              <path d="M7 17 17 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>smart-mqtt</h3>
          <p>一款面向物联网领域的 MQTT 消息中间件产品</p>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="explore-link">
              探索项目
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://smartboot.tech/redisun/" target="_blank" class="ecosystem-card">
        <div class="card-border"></div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="project-tag">Redis</span>
            <svg class="arrow-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M7 7h10v10"/>
              <path d="M7 17 17 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Redisun</h3>
          <p>基于 smart-socket 开发的轻量级 Redis 客户端，专为 Java 平台设计，支持异步非阻塞 I/O 操作</p>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="explore-link">
              探索项目
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ecosystem-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .ecosystem-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-color), transparent);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #ec4899;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #ec4899;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(1.1); }
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .section-badge {
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .ecosystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ecosystem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .ecosystem-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, transparent);
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover .card-border {
    opacity: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-secondary), var(--accent-primary));
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) - 1px);
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ecosystem-card.featured .card-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05));
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .project-tag {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .arrow-icon {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover .arrow-icon {
    transform: translate(3px, -3px);
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .ecosystem-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
    transition: color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover h3 {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .ecosystem-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-footer {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .explore-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .explore-link svg {
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover .explore-link {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .ecosystem-card:hover .explore-link svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
